                </p>
                <p>
                    They are given multiple opportunities to interact and hear valuable insights from bureaucrats, industry experts, public servants, and influential functionaries.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b>Come – let the experts at EduInstitute Academy guide you towards a bright future in the administrative sector of the nation.<br>
                    Hon. Rajendra Singh – IPS</b>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="vm-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Vision and Mission</h2>
        <div class="row g-4 mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-right">
                <div class="vm-card">
                    <h4>Vision</h4>
                    <p>"Producing an eminent center of excellence in IAS coaching and training to attract more and efficient youth to transform themselves into future civil servants."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                <div class="vm-card">
                    <h4>Mission</h4>
                    <p>"Become a prominent and foremost institute of IAS coaching and training to help create disciplined and competent Civil Service professionals."</p>
